qas.question: how to resolve this error <Text>An error occurred whilst parsing with DFDL</Text> <Text>CTDP3002E: Unexpected data found at offset '44754' after parsing completed. Data: '0x55...'.</Text> ?

answers.text: 1. Goto RFHUTIL 2. Select Queue manager and Queue name 3. Take Backup and if those are trigger messages then purge the queue, else reprocess the messages in to input queue.
